flowchart TD
    Start([Student Login]) --> Dashboard[View Dashboard<br/>Status Window]
    Dashboard --> Choice{What to do?}

    Choice -->|Learn| Tutor[Chat with AI Tutor<br/>Ask Questions]
    Choice -->|Complete| Quests[View Active Quests<br/>Assignments]
    Choice -->|Track| Progress[View Progress<br/>XP & Mastery]
    Choice -->|Explore| Codex[Browse Codex<br/>Curriculum Tree]

    Tutor --> Ask[Ask Question<br/>Get Cited Answer]
    Quests --> Attempt[Attempt Quest<br/>Answer Questions]
    Progress --> Review[Review Mastery<br/>Check Streak]
    Codex --> Learn[Explore Topics<br/>Related Concepts]

    Ask --> Sources[View Sources<br/>Verify Citations]
    Attempt --> Submit[Submit Answers<br/>Wait for Grading]
    Review --> Goals[Set New Goals<br/>Track Achievements]
    Learn --> Ask

    Sources --> Continue{Continue Learning?}
    Submit --> Feedback[View Feedback<br/>Check Score]
    Goals --> Continue
    Feedback --> Continue

    Continue -->|Yes| Choice
    Continue -->|No| End([Logout])

    style Start fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style Tutor fill:#10b981,color:#fff
    style Quests fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff
    style Progress fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
    style End fill:#6b7280,color:#fff
